<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針條毛咩 最驚俾人用針拮"},{"pid":"a47ef82c4620fbf2f25f9080356549d9ec70a5df","tid":306880,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bbb6c36f1ef332b4261347bc1c11cc451839719","tid":306880,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"得一次實驗，得幾個月，人數得72個，顯著成效得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係唔信針灸，但個所謂實驗兒戲到咁，都仲夠膽攞個結果出嚟曬命？"},{"pid":"6cb9f8d1614d2f5682081cc0247a367c0927bc2b","tid":306880,"uid":36911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得一次實驗，得幾個月，人數得72個，顯著成效得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係唔信針灸，但個所謂實驗兒戲到咁，都仲夠膽攞個結果出嚟曬命？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8星期後體重平均降低2.47公斤（約5.4磅），BMI下跌0.19。</span><br />\n唔洗運動仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e02d3897ccd82190d9576a6a7a8b75f5c4398a7","tid":306880,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"抑制食慾抑制食慾抑制食慾"},{"pid":"fea7f7449e2900dad0307386378cb42c60e53387","tid":306880,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過往多份醫學文獻提出針灸能夠透過刺激神經系統，增加血清素及安多酚兩種神經傳遞物分泌，達到抑制食欲、增加分解脂肪速度等效果<br />\n<br />\n講到尾都係離唔開食少左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  垃圾中醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e8c81ff7bc8d6c66860151cac1844be4310db2","tid":306880,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"針灸減肥係大陸醫院直頭當專科咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過中醫師變美容師梗係覺得77地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2424694a90e503aae433960d787260f833c3be24","tid":